. Hence, we can obtain the gauge potential using relation $A_{t}\left(
r\right) =\int F_{rt}dr$ as
\begin{eqnarray}
A_{t} &=&\mu +\frac{qb^{2z-2}(2n-2)^{(z-n-1)/(2n-2)}}{
(2-z)^{(-5+3n+z)/(2n-2)}}\left( \frac{q^{2}l^{2z-2}}{\beta ^{2}}\right)
^{\left( 3-n-z\right) /\left( 2n-2\right) }  \notag \\
