&&\left. -(z-2)\left[ \Gamma \left( \frac{z+n-3}{2n-2},\frac{2-z}{2n-2}
L_{W}\left( \varrho \right) \right) -\Gamma \left( \frac{z+n-3}{2n-2}\right) 
\right] \right\} .  \label{At}
\end{eqnarray}
It is remarkable to note that since from one side $L_{W}\left( \varrho
\right) \rightarrow 0$ as $r\rightarrow \infty $ and from another side $
